                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <p class="text-gray-700">Gestión de trazabilidad y seguimiento de lotes mediante códigos QR</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <p class="text-gray-700">Facturación y cumplimiento de obligaciones fiscales</p>
